#: app/templates/about.html:10
msgid "About Grylli"
msgstr "Dwar Grylli"

#: app/templates/about.html:13
msgid ""
"Grylli is a secure, self-hosted message delivery platform that automatically"
" sends pre-configured messages if a user fails to check in within a defined "
"time period."
msgstr ""
"Grylli huwa pjattaforma sigura, ospitata waħedha għall-kunsinna tal-messaġġi"
" li awtomatikament tibgħat messaġġi kkonfigurati minn qabel jekk utent "
"jonqos milli jivverifika f'perjodu ta' żmien definit."

#: app/templates/about.html:14
msgid ""
"It supports multiple users, customizable schedules, and recurring reminders."
msgstr "Jappoġġja multipli utenti u skedi personalizzabbli."

#: app/templates/about.html:15
msgid ""
"Messages and reminders can be delivered via email, webhooks, or over 100 "
"third-party services through Apprise."
msgstr ""
"Il-messaġġi jistgħu jiġu kkonsenjati permezz ta' email, webhooks, jew fuq "
"aktar minn 80 servizz ta' partijiet terzi permezz ta' Apprise."

#: app/templates/about.html:16
msgid ""
"Users can configure their own SMTP servers to ensure emails and reminders "
"appear to come directly from them — not from the system administrator."
msgstr ""
"L-utenti jistgħu jikkonfiguraw is-servers SMTP tagħhom biex jiżguraw li "
"l-messaġġi jidhru li ġejjin direttament minnhom — mhux mis-sistema "
"amministrattiva."

#: app/templates/about.html:17
msgid ""
"Sensitive data is encrypted at rest, and all operations are secured with "
"strong authentication and audit-friendly logging."
msgstr ""
"Dejta sensittiva hija kkodifikata meta mhix fil-moviment, u "
"l-operazzjonijiet kollha tal-messaġġi huma siguri b’awtentikazzjoni "
"b’saħħitha u loggjar li jiffavorixxi l-awditjar."

#: app/templates/about.html:18
msgid ""
"Built with a modern, reactive technology stack, Grylli is optimized for "
"responsiveness and works seamlessly across desktop and mobile devices."
msgstr ""
"Mibni b’teknoloġija moderna, reattiva, Grylli huwa ottimizzat għar-"
"risponsività u jaħdem bla xkiel fuq apparati desktop u mobbli."

