"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Grylli jinkludi istruzzjonijiet mibnija fl-app biex jgħinuk tikkonfigura u "
"timmaniġġja s-setup tiegħek."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Din il-paġna tipprovdi ħarsa ġenerali tal-karatteristiċi ewlenin u links "
"diretti għall-postijiet fejn jistgħu jiġu mmaniġġjati."

