msgid "View and manage secure email messages"
msgstr "Ħarsa ġenerali tal-messaġġi tal-email sikuri"

#: app/templates/help.html:38
msgid "Security"
msgstr "🔐 Sigurtà"

#: app/templates/help.html:39
msgid "Grylli encrypts sensitive data and logs all key actions for auditing."
msgstr ""
"Grylli jikkripta dejta sensittiva u jirrekordja l-azzjonijiet ewlenin kollha"
" għal skopijiet ta' awditjar."

#: app/templates/index.html:9 app/views/locale.py:95
msgid "Welcome to Grylli"
msgstr "Merħba għal Grylli"

#: app/templates/index.html:11
msgid "Pronounced"
msgstr "Pronunzja"

#: app/templates/index.html:11
msgid "like “grill-ee”"
msgstr "bħal “grill-ee”"

#: app/templates/index.html:14
msgid ""
"Grylli is a secure message scheduling and delivery system designed to ensure"
" your important messages are delivered — even if you can’t be there to send "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Grylli huwa sistema sigura ta' skedar u twassil ta' messaġġi ddisinjata biex"
" tiżgura li l-messaġġi importanti tiegħek jiġu twassla — anki jekk ma tistax"
" tkun hemm biex tibagħathom."

#: app/templates/index.html:17
msgid ""
"Whether you’re planning ahead, setting up emergency communication, or "
"building peace of mind, Grylli helps automate your message delivery via "
"multiple channels including email, webhooks, and Apprise notifications."
msgstr ""
"Kemm jekk qed tippjana l-quddiem, twaqqaf komunikazzjoni ta' emerġenza, jew "
"tibni l-paċi tal-moħħ, Grylli jgħinek awtomatizza t-twassil tal-messaġġi "
"tiegħek permezz tal-email, webhooks, jew notifikazzjonijiet Apprise jekk "
"titlef check-in."

#: app/templates/index.html:19
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "Bidu"

#: app/templates/index.html:21
msgid "Create a message, email, or reminder."
msgstr "Oħloq messaġġ jew email."

#: app/templates/index.html:22
msgid "Set your check-in interval and grace period (for messages)."
msgstr "Issettja l-intervall tal-check-in tiegħek u l-perjodu ta' grazzja."

#: app/templates/index.html:23
msgid "Assign one or more delivery destinations."
msgstr "Assenja waħda jew aktar destinazzjonijiet ta' twassil."

#: app/templates/index.html:24
msgid "Optionally attach files for secure emails."
msgstr "F'għażla, jgħaqqad fajls għal emails sikuri."

#: app/templates/index.html:25
msgid "Schedule reminders to send at specific times or on a recurring basis."
msgstr ""
"Skeda tfakkira biex jintbagħtu f'ħinijiet speċifiċi jew fuq bażi rikurrenti."

#: app/templates/index.html:26
msgid "Enable the message or reminder to activate delivery."
msgstr "Enebla l-messaġġ jew tfakkira biex tattiva l-kunsinna."

#: app/templates/index.html:28
msgid ""
"Regularly check in to Grylli to prevent automated delivery; miss a check-in "
"and Grylli sends your messages as scheduled."
msgstr ""
"Iċċekkja b'mod regolari f'Grylli biex tipprevjeni l-kunsinna awtomatika; "
"jekk titlif check-in, Grylli jibgħat il-messaġġi tiegħek kif skedat."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:10
msgid "Privacy Notice"
msgstr "Avviż tal-Privatezza"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:13
msgid ""
"Grylli respects your privacy and is designed to minimize the collection and "
"storage of personal data."
msgstr ""
"Grylli jirrispetta l-privatezza tiegħek u huwa mfassal biex jimminimizza "
"l-ġbir u l-ħażna ta’ data personali."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:14
msgid ""
"All data is encrypted where appropriate and remains fully under your control"
" if you self-host this platform."
msgstr ""
"Id-data kollha hija ikkriptata fejn xieraq u tibqa' kompletament taħt il-"
"kontroll tiegħek jekk tospita lilek innifsek din il-pjattaforma."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:17
msgid "What Data We Collect"
msgstr "X'informazzjoni Nġabru"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:19
msgid "Email address and password hash (for authentication)"
msgstr "Indirizz tal-email u password hash (għal awtentikazzjoni)"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:20
msgid "Optional MFA secret and recovery codes (encrypted at rest)"
msgstr ""
"Sigriet tal-MFA fakultattiv u kodiċijiet ta’ rkupru (ikkriptati fi stat "
"staġnat)"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:21
msgid "Reminder and message content you configure"
msgstr "Kontenut ta’ rimindjar u messaġġ li tikkonfigura"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:22
msgid "User-specific settings, SMTP configuration (if provided)"
msgstr "Settings speċifiċi għall-utent, konfigurazzjoni SMTP (jekk ipprovdut)"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:25
msgid "How Your Data Is Used"
msgstr "Kif Tintuża d-Dwara Tiegħek"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:27
msgid ""
"Your data is used solely for the purpose of delivering reminders and "
"messages according to your preferences."
msgstr ""
"Id-data tiegħek tintuża biss għall-iskop li tgħaddi l-rimindji u l-messaġġi "
"skont il-preferenzi tiegħek."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:28
msgid ""
"Grylli does not share, sell, or transmit your personal data to any third "
"parties."
msgstr ""
"Grylli ma jaqsamx, ibigħx, jew jirritrav.cssir id-dat personali tiegħek lil "
"xi partijiet terzi."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:31
msgid "Your Rights"
msgstr "Id-Drittijiet Tiegħek"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:33
msgid ""
"You can export all of your data at any time from the Account Settings page."
msgstr ""
"Tista' tesporta d-data tiegħek kollha fi kwalunkwe ħin mill-paġna tas-"
"Settings tal-Kont."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:34
msgid "You may permanently delete your account and all associated data."
msgstr "Ma tistax tħassar il-kont tiegħek għax int l-aħħar amministratur."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:35
msgid ""
"If you are using a self-hosted instance, contact the instance administrator "
"for data inquiries."
msgstr ""
"Jekk qed tuża istanza li tospita lilek innifsek, ikkuntattja lill-"
"amministratur tal-istanza għal mistoqsijiet dwar id-data."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:38
msgid "Self-Hosting Responsibility"
msgstr "Responsabbiltà tal-Ostjaljar lil-Lilek Innifsek"

#: app/templates/privacy.html:40
msgid ""
"If you are running Grylli on your own server, you are responsible for the "
"storage, processing, and lawful handling of all user data on that instance."
msgstr ""
"Jekk qed tmexxi Grylli fuq is-server tiegħek, int responsabbli għall-ħażna, "
"proċessar, u trattament legali tad-data kollha tal-utent fuq dik l-istanza."

#: app/templates/privacy.html:44
msgid ""
"This notice was last updated in June 2025 and may evolve to reflect changes "
"in the software or regulatory landscape."
msgstr ""
"Dan l-avviż ġie aġġornat l-aħħar f'Ġunju 2025 u jista’ jevolvi biex "
"jirrifletti bidliet fis-softwer jew fil-pajsaġġ regolatorju."

